snippet.title: Arcade Longplay - Gorf (1981) Midway
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the arcade game Gorf. The game is very good vertical shooter with variety of levels resembling other games from the times, like Invaders (Astro Battler), Galaxian, Laser  Command and other.
